{
  "video_id": "hQltlSDNmd0",
  "title": "How Pakistani women are taking the internet back | Nighat Dad",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13122.0,
      "end_time": 15663.0,
      "text": "Imagine waking up to a stranger --"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15687.0,
      "end_time": 18133.0,
      "text": "sometimes multiple strangers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18939.0,
      "end_time": 21777.0,
      "text": "questioning your right to existence"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21801.0,
      "end_time": 24121.0,
      "text": "for something that you wrote online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25480.0,
      "end_time": 28801.0,
      "text": "waking up to an angry message,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28825.0,
      "end_time": 31120.0,
      "text": "scared and worried for your safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31975.0,
      "end_time": 34658.0,
      "text": "Welcome to the world of cyberharassment."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35344.0,
      "end_time": 39275.0,
      "text": "The kind of harassment that women face in Pakistan is very serious"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39299.0,
      "end_time": 42327.0,
      "text": "and leads to sometimes deadly outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43660.0,
      "end_time": 46390.0,
      "text": "This kind of harassment keeps women from accessing the internet --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46414.0,
      "end_time": 48191.0,
      "text": "essentially, knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48926.0,
      "end_time": 51217.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a form of oppression."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52819.0,
      "end_time": 56508.0,
      "text": "Pakistan is the sixth most populous country in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56532.0,
      "end_time": 60355.0,
      "text": "with 140 million people having access to mobile technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60380.0,
      "end_time": 63970.0,
      "text": "and 15 percent internet penetration."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65256.0,
      "end_time": 69479.0,
      "text": "And this number doesn&#39;t seem to go down with the rise of new technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70270.0,
      "end_time": 75559.0,
      "text": "Pakistan is also the birthplace of the youngest Nobel Peace Prize winner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75583.0,
      "end_time": 76942.0,
      "text": "Malala Yousafzai."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 78438.0,
      "end_time": 81210.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s just one aspect of Pakistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 81961.0,
      "end_time": 86124.0,
      "text": "Another aspect is where the twisted concept of honor"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 86148.0,
      "end_time": 89390.0,
      "text": "is linked to women and their bodies;"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 89924.0,
      "end_time": 93159.0,
      "text": "where men are allowed to disrespect women"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93183.0,
      "end_time": 95000.0,
      "text": "and even kill them sometimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95240.0,
      "end_time": 97653.0,
      "text": "in the name of so-called \"family honor\";"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 98522.0,
      "end_time": 103710.0,
      "text": "where women are left to die right outside their houses"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103950.0,
      "end_time": 105683.0,
      "text": "for speaking to a man on a mobile phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105707.0,
      "end_time": 107577.0,
      "text": "in the name of \"family honor.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108158.0,
      "end_time": 109929.0,
      "text": "Let me say this very clearly:"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 110681.0,
      "end_time": 112146.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not honor;"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 112170.0,
      "end_time": 114526.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a cold-blooded murder."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117551.0,
      "end_time": 121702.0,
      "text": "I come from a very small village in Punjab, Pakistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 121726.0,
      "end_time": 126600.0,
      "text": "where women are not allowed to pursue their higher education."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 127308.0,
      "end_time": 131220.0,
      "text": "The elders of my extended family didn&#39;t allow their women"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131450.0,
      "end_time": 134908.0,
      "text": "to pursue their higher education or their professional careers."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 134932.0,
      "end_time": 139580.0,
      "text": "However, unlike the other male guardians of my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 139820.0,
      "end_time": 144566.0,
      "text": "my father was one who really supported my ambitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 145941.0,
      "end_time": 147627.0,
      "text": "To get my law degree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 148344.0,
      "end_time": 152257.0,
      "text": "of course, it was really difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 152281.0,
      "end_time": 156494.0,
      "text": "and [there were] frowns of disapproval."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157373.0,
      "end_time": 160867.0,
      "text": "But in the end, I knew it&#39;s either me or them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 160891.0,
      "end_time": 162268.0,
      "text": "and I chose myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 164446.0,
      "end_time": 169700.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 170673.0,
      "end_time": 173832.0,
      "text": "My family&#39;s traditions and expectations for a woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 173856.0,
      "end_time": 176777.0,
      "text": "wouldn&#39;t allow me to own a mobile phone until I was married."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 177544.0,
      "end_time": 179627.0,
      "text": "And even when I was married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 179651.0,
      "end_time": 183738.0,
      "text": "this tool became a tool for my own surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 184923.0,
      "end_time": 189353.0,
      "text": "When I resisted this idea of being surveilled by my ex-husband,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 189377.0,
      "end_time": 191660.0,
      "text": "he really didn&#39;t approve of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 191900.0,
      "end_time": 193174.0,
      "text": "and threw me out of his house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 193198.0,
      "end_time": 196570.0,
      "text": "along with my six-month-old son, Abdullah."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 197436.0,
      "end_time": 201755.0,
      "text": "And that was the time when I first asked myself, \"Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 201779.0,
      "end_time": 205525.0,
      "text": "Why are women not allowed to enjoy the same equal rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 205549.0,
      "end_time": 207525.0,
      "text": "enshrined in our Constitution?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 208631.0,
      "end_time": 212581.0,
      "text": "While the law states that a woman has the same equal access"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 212605.0,
      "end_time": 214340.0,
      "text": "to the information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 214580.0,
      "end_time": 217837.0,
      "text": "why is it always men -- brothers, fathers and husbands --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 217861.0,
      "end_time": 219899.0,
      "text": "who are granting these rights to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 219924.0,
      "end_time": 222772.0,
      "text": "effectively making the law irrelevant?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 224801.0,
      "end_time": 226558.0,
      "text": "So I decided to take a step,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 226582.0,
      "end_time": 229549.0,
      "text": "instead of keep questioning these patriarchal structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 229573.0,
      "end_time": 230892.0,
      "text": "and societal norms."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 231656.0,
      "end_time": 235636.0,
      "text": "And I founded the Digital Rights Foundation in 2012"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 235660.0,
      "end_time": 242112.0,
      "text": "to address all the issues and women&#39;s experiences in online spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 242136.0,
      "end_time": 243600.0,
      "text": "and cyberharassment."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 244990.0,
      "end_time": 248917.0,
      "text": "From lobbying for free and safe internet"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 248941.0,
      "end_time": 250404.0,
      "text": "to convincing young women"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 250428.0,
      "end_time": 255654.0,
      "text": "that access to the safe internet is their fundamental, basic, human right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 255678.0,
      "end_time": 258608.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m trying to play my part in igniting the spark"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 258632.0,
      "end_time": 262247.0,
      "text": "to address the questions that have bothered me all these years."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 262955.0,
      "end_time": 264808.0,
      "text": "With a hope in my heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 264832.0,
      "end_time": 267397.0,
      "text": "and to offer a solution to this menace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 267422.0,
      "end_time": 271804.0,
      "text": "I started Pakistan&#39;s and the region&#39;s first cyberharassment help line"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 271828.0,
      "end_time": 273643.0,
      "text": "in December 2016 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 273668.0,
      "end_time": 279409.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 280380.0,
      "end_time": 284311.0,
      "text": "to extend my support to the women who do not know who to turn to"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 284335.0,
      "end_time": 287180.0,
      "text": "when they face serious threats online."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 287757.0,
      "end_time": 291767.0,
      "text": "I think of the women who do not have the necessary support"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 291791.0,
      "end_time": 297344.0,
      "text": "to deal with the mental trauma when they feel unsafe in online spaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 297369.0,
      "end_time": 299452.0,
      "text": "and they go about their daily activities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 299476.0,
      "end_time": 302719.0,
      "text": "thinking that there is a rape threat in their in-box."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 303329.0,
      "end_time": 307491.0,
      "text": "Safe access to the internet is an access to knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 307515.0,
      "end_time": 309342.0,
      "text": "and knowledge is freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 309367.0,
      "end_time": 311485.0,
      "text": "When I fight for women&#39;s digital rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 311509.0,
      "end_time": 313381.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m fighting for equality."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 313405.0,
      "end_time": 314556.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 314580.0,
      "end_time": 316522.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}